/**
 * base-ui.ts — Merged extension: custom footer, dev-vibes, side-by-side diff
 *
 * Combines three extensions into one:
 *   • Custom footer with pwd, model, thinking level, and context meter
 *   • Fun random working messages on agent/turn start
 *   • Side-by-side diff rendering for the edit tool
 *
 * Usage: drop in ~/.pi/agent/extensions/ and /reload
